{"article_id":"GC1FA9qHn8KsGj0q","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump announced early Wednesday morning on Twitter","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that Secretary of State Mike Pompeo was on his way back to the U.S. from North Korea with three Americans","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"who had been released from prison by the isolated totalitarian state .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Mr. Trump had hinted over the past week","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that the three men would soon be released ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"but only Tuesday did he announce Pompeo 's trip to North Korea","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"-- ostensibly to work out the details of his upcoming summit with Kim Jong Un .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"`` They seem to be in good health .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Also , good meeting with Kim Jong Un .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Date & Place set , ''","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Mr. Trump added in his tweet .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"I am pleased to inform you","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that Secretary of State Mike Pompeo is in the air and on his way back from North Korea with the 3 wonderful gentlemen","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"that everyone is looking so forward to meeting .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"They seem to be in good health .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Also , good meeting with Kim Jong Un .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Date & Place set .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"May 9 , 2018","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Pompeo and his `` guests '' would land at Joint Base Andrews , outside Washington D.C. , at 2 a.m. Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and that he would `` be there","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"to greet them .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Very exciting ! ''","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"In a written statement , the White House said","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"`` President Trump appreciates leader Kim Jong Un 's action","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to release these American citizens ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and views this as a positive gesture of goodwill .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"The three Americans appear to be in good condition","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"and were all able to walk on the plane","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"without assistance . ''","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence issued a statement on Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"crediting `` President Trump 's tough minded diplomacy ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"with winning the release of the three men ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"the administration was `` encouraged '' by it ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"but warning ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` we will not let off the pressure","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"until we achieve full denuclearization '' of North Korea .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Secretary Pompeo and his \" guests \" will be landing at Andrews Air Force Base at 2:00 A.M. in the morning .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"I will be there","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"to greet them .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Very exciting !","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"May 9 , 2018","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"The longest-imprisoned of the three U.S. nationals , Kim Dong Chul , was sentenced in April 2016 to 10 years hard labor for espionage .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"The two others","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"-- Kim Hak Song and Tony Kim --","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"were working at the Pyongyang University of Science and Technology","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"when they were detained about a year ago .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"The university said Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that it was , `` very grateful to learn of the release of the three US-Korean citizens , ''","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"that `` all three men have been daily in our thoughts ;","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"and our hopes and prayers have been fulfilled by their release . ''","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Tony Kim 's family thanked Mr. Trump in a statement","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"released Wednesday morning ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"saying :","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"`` We are very grateful for the release of our husband and father , Tony Kim , and the other two American detainees .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"We want to thank all of those","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"who have worked toward and contributed to his return home .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"We also want to thank the President","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"for engaging directly with North Korea .","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"Mostly , we thank God for Tony 's safe return . ''","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Their release comes","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"as Mr. Trump and North Korean leader Kim Jong Un prepare to hold a summit","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"-- possibly within weeks .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Kim and South Korean President Moon Jae-in held a historic meeting in the Demilitarized Zone on April 27 ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"agreeing to work toward denuclearizing the Korean Peninsula","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"and discussing plans","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to declare a formal end to the Korean War .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Pompeo confirmed in a tweet of his own later Wednesday morning","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that he had met with Kim while in Pyongyang .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"he had `` productive meetings '' with the North Korean leader ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"but did not confirm Mr. Trump 's earlier tweet","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"the time and place for the summit had been confirmed .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"I had productive meetings in Pyongyang with Chairman Kim Jong-un","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"and made progress .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"I 'm delighted to bring home three Americans .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"- Secretary Pompeo","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"( @ SecPompeo )","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"May 9 , 2018","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"Very little is known about why the three men were actually detained by North Korea ,","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"or what conditions they faced in custody .","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"Below is a brief summary of what information was made available on the three men .","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"Kim , a South Korean-born U.S. citizen , has been held the longest .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"The former Virginia resident was sentenced in April 2016 to 10 years in prison with hard labor","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"after being convicted of espionage .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"He reportedly ran a trade and hotel service company in Rason , a special economic zone on North Korea 's border with Russia .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Kim worked in agricultural development at an experimental farm run by the Pyongyang University of Science and Technology .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"The university is the only privately funded college in North Korea","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"and was founded in 2010 with donations from Christian groups .","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"He was detained last May for alleged anti-state activities .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"The North 's official Korean Central News Agency announced","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"that Kim was detained","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"and that `` a relevant institution is now conducting detailed investigation into his crimes . ''","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"Tony Kim , 59 ,","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"who also uses the name Kim Sang-duk ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"was detained a year ago at the Pyongyang airport .","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"He had been teaching at the Pyongyang University of Science and Technology , as had Kim Hak Song .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"He was accused of committing unspecified criminal acts","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"intended to overthrow the government .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"The North has not said","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"whether the two cases of staff at the university are connected .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"In April 2017 , the chancellor of the university said","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"Kim taught accounting at the university for about a month","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"and previously taught at a university in China .","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"he was informed that the detention had `` nothing to do '' with Kim 's work at the university ,","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"but he did not know anything further .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"North Korea only officially confirmed the detention of Kim in May 2017 .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Kim 's son , Sol Kim , told","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"he was stunned by his father 's detention .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"`` I asked myself","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"why , what happened ,","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"what is the reason ,","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"lots of different thoughts went through my head .","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"Will I see him again ? ''","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"`` Part of me really thought","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"he did not do anything wrong ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"he wo n't be held very long . ''","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"There were unconfirmed reports","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"that the detainees were moved last week from prisons to a hotel in or near the capital , Pyongyang .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"asked on May 3 about their possible release ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"White House Press Secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders hedged ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"it `` would be an incredible sign of goodwill ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"and certainly a great statement for the North Koreans","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"to make ahead of the summit and the discussions , ''","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"but that she had no announcement at the time .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"Speaking to reporters on Tuesday ,","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"he 'd be meeting with senior North Korean leaders","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"but did n't know","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"if he 'd meet with Kim .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"`` We 're prepared to meet with anyone","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"who is speaking on behalf of the North Korean government","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"and can give us solid answers","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"so we 're prepared , ''","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"`` We have been asking for the release of these detainees for this administration for 17 months , ''","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"he told reporters on Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"`` We 'll talk about it again today .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"it 'd be a great gesture","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"if they would choose to do so . ''","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"Pompeo secretly met with Kim in April","depth":4},{"id":153,"text":"while he was still director of the CIA .","depth":4},{"id":154,"text":"He was confirmed and sworn in as secretary of state on April 26","depth":4},{"id":155,"text":"and quickly departed on his first foreign trip to Europe and the Middle East .","depth":4},{"id":156,"text":"The release of the three Americans comes","depth":4},{"id":157,"text":"11 months after another American detainee , 22-year-old college student Otto Warmbier , was sent home from North Korea in a coma .","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"Warmbier never recovered consciousness","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"and died a week later .","depth":6},{"id":160,"text":"Warmbier was detained in January 2016","depth":5},{"id":161,"text":"while visiting North Korea at the end of a five-day tour .","depth":5},{"id":162,"text":"He was later sentenced to 15 years hard labor","depth":5},{"id":163,"text":"for allegedly stealing a propaganda banner at his hotel .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":327,"left":315,"right":326,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":315,"left":210,"right":314,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":183,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":166,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":0,"right":165,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":165,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":169,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":167,"right":168,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":167,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":172,"right":180,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":172,"left":171,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":7,"right":170,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":177,"right":179,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":174,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":11,"right":173,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":173,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":14,"right":175,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"N